'''Charles Mensah'''  yari umukinnyi wa firime wa [[Gabon]], umwanditsi wa sinema akaba n'umuyobozi ushinzwe umusaruro<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/charles-mensah/5990</ref>. Azwi cyane ku izina rya "The Gentleman of African Cinemas", Mensah yagize uruhare muri documentaire nyinshi zamamaye cyane nka ''Équateur'', ''Les Couilles de l'éléphant'' na ''Lybek, ipfunwe ry'abazima'' <ref>https://myastro.com/myastropedia/charles-mensah</ref>.  Yakoze nk'umuntu uharanira iterambere rya sinema yigenga yo mu majyepfo mu mwuga umaze imyaka irenga mirongo itatu<ref>https://mubi.com/cast/charles-mensah</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1948 i Omboué, muri [[Gabon]] . Yapfuye ku ya 3 Kamena 2011, afite imyaka 63.<ref>https://www.flickr.com/photos/eu_development/3421413904</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1976, yakoze ibihimbano bye bya mbere, ''Obali'' afatanya na Pierre-Marie Ndong. Hanyuma mu 1977 yakoze umushinga wa kabiri ''Ayouma'' afatanya na Ndong na Patience Dabany<ref>https://www.afrik.com/charles-mensah-ou-l-ambition-d-un-cinema-africain-par-les-africains</ref>. Intsinzi yo gukora amafilime, Mensah yagize uruhare mu gutunganya, kuri iyi nshuro hamwe na filime ''Équateur'', yasinyiye Serge Gainsbourg<ref>https://www.union.sonapresse.com/personnalites-gabonaises/charles-mensah-la-vie-est-un-film-au-commencement-etait-limage-14446</ref> . Hamwe n’umukinnyi wa filime uzwi cyane Henri-Joseph Koumba Bididi mu 1995, Mensah yagize uruhare muri televiziyo ''L'Auberge du Salut'', filime yuzuye ya Gabon.<ref>https://www.franceculture.fr/personne-charles-mensah.html</ref> 

Nkumuproducer, Mensah yitabiriye ibikorwa byinshi birimo: ''Le Damier de Balufu Bakupu Kanyinda'' mu 1996, ''Dôlè (l'Argent)'' na Imunga Iwanga mu 2000<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/charles-mensah/5990</ref>, ''Les Couilles de l'éléphant'' mu 2001 na ''N'Djamena City'' iyobowe na Issa Serge Coelo mu 2006. Yagize kandi uruhare muri documentaire ngufi kuri ''Lybek, le crunch du vivant'' <ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/charles-mensah-1</ref>. Kugeza mu 2009, yari afite umwanya wo kuba Umuyobozi mukuru w'ikigo cy'igihugu cya Sinema ya Gabon (CENACI)<ref>http://www.bdpgabon.org/articles/2011/06/03/gabon-le-cineaste-charles-mensah-tire-sa-reverence/</ref>, ubu kikaba kizwi ku izina rya Gabonese Institute of Image and Sound (IGIS). Muri uwo mwaka, yabaye perezida w’ishyirahamwe ry’abakora amafilime muri Pan-[[Afurika]] (FEPACI) ndetse no muri komisiyo ishinzwe ikigega cyo gufasha amafilime y’umuryango mpuzamahanga w’igifaransa. Muri 2011<ref>http://africultures.com/murmures/?no=7419</ref>, yakoraga muri Bididi's ''Le collier du Makoko'' yamenyekanye ku rwego mpuzamahanga harimo na Cannes <ref>https://fr.allafrica.com/stories/200703200368.html</ref>.  

